# 关于

{% highlight java %}
import java.util.Calendar;

public class AboutMe {
	public static void main(String[] args) {
		About me = new About();
		Calendar c = Calendar.getInstance();
		me.name = "{{ site.author.name }}";
		String[] description = {"辍学生", "Android学习者", "GoogleFans"};
		me.born = 1997;
		me.age = c.get(Calendar.YEAR) - me.born;
		me.company = null;
		me.email = "{{ site.author.email }}";
		me.blog = "{{ site.blog.url }}";
		me.weibo = "{{ site.author.weibo }}";
		me.github = "{{ site.author.github }}";
		
		System.out.println("Name: " + me.name);
		for (String s: description) {
			if (s == description[0]) {
				System.out.printf("Description: %s, ", s);
				continue;
			}
			if (s == description[description.length - 1]) {
				System.out.printf("%s\n", s);
				break;
			}
			System.out.printf("%s, ", s);
		}
		System.out.println("Born: " + me.born);
		System.out.println("Age: " + me.age);
		System.out.println("Company: " + me.company);
		System.out.println("E-mail: " + me.email);
		System.out.println("Blog: " + "http://" + me.blog);
		System.out.println("Weibo: " + me.weibo);
		System.out.println("GitHub: " + me.github + "\n");
		
		while(me.isLife()) {
			learning();
			reading();
			thinking();
			me.age++;
		}
	}
	
	private static void learning() {
		System.out.println("Learning physics knowledge.");
	}
	private static void reading() {
		System.out.println("Reading books of interest.");
	}
	private static void thinking() {
		System.out.println("Thinking about the meaning of life." + "\n");
	}
}

class About {
	public String name;
	public int age;
	public int born;
	public String company;
	public String blog;
	public String email;
	public String weibo;
	public String github;
	
	public boolean isLife() {
		return age < 100 ? true : false;
	}
}
